
 C++2LaTeX-l: Produce prettyprinted LaTeX files from  C++ or C sources
              for use in literate programs formatted with noweb

 Copyright (C) 1996 Francisco J. Ballesteros <nemo@nautilus> for the
                    literate (-l) version

NOTE: This literate version does not include code from the plain
c++2latex distribution but I still consider this program a derivative
from the original one, at least in spirit ;-) -- nemo@nautilus 
